===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[wager]], an agreement between two parties that a stake (usually money) will be paid by the loser to the winner &nbsp; the one who correctly forecast the outcome of an event.
# A degree of [[certainty]].
#: ''It’s a good '''bet''' that it will rain tomorrow.''
#: ''It’s an even '''bet''' that Jim will come top of the maths test tomorrow''

